
    Blac Chyna called out for skin-lightening cream

        

    
        
                
                Image copyright
                 Getty Images
                
            
            
        Blac Chyna is being criticised for selling a skin-lightening cream in Nigeria.The model's new product, in partnership with a brand called Whitenicious, was announced on Instagram.The Whitenicious x Blac Chyna Collection is described as an "illuminating and brightening cream" that "lightens without bleaching skin out".Some skin lightening products are banned in the UK.
    
        
